title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Aug 27 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Aug 27 2022
description:
Portland, Oregon, once among the safest U.S. cities, has quadrupled its homicide rate. Oregon’s largest city shows the difficulty law enforcement faces in trying to curb violent crime in liberal-controlled cities. Julie Kelly joins Clay and Buck with the latest on the FBI Whitmer kidnapping conspiracy, the Mar-a-Lago raid and "105%" chance the Department of Justice will indict Trump.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
